        "app_name": "Age of the monster",
        "release_date": "1980-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
        "description": "Through a succession of time jumps from the 70s to a post-anthropocene future, meet the Verdeau family and their pavilion on the banks of the Rhône. In this poetic experience, we follow in the footsteps of a mysterious and peaceful creature with whom we journey across eras, thus experiencing time on a scale that dwarfs human society. By following the monster, a symbol of the river’s rebirth, and by leaving their familiar environment, the user is invited to rethink their relationship with the living world.\nDirected by Benjamin Nuel, creator of Isle of the Dead, winner of the Best VR Award in Venice in 2018, AGE OF THE MONSTER is an interactive and dreamlike experience.",
